4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper does not explicitly use neural or evolutionary computing, but the methods used in the paper may be applicable to these domains. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper does not explicitly deal with data structures and algorithms, but the methods used in the paper involve calculations and transformations that may be of interest to this sub-category.
